A photorealistic aerial view of a rustic Bavarian mountain hut perched on an alpine meadow in early autumn, with the dramatic limestone peaks of the German Alps rising in the background under a crisp blue sky with wispy clouds. In the valley below, a fairytale castle with white limestone walls and slender towers catches golden afternoon sunlight. The foreground shows weathered wooden tables on an outdoor terrace with checkered tablecloths, empty beer steins, and remnants of a celebration. Pine forests carpet the mountainsides in deep green, while patches of early snow dust the highest peaks. The air appears crystal clear, conveying the freshness of alpine atmosphere contrasting with distant humid lowlands.
